@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_uebdhc(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (0.90 + 0.15)
    v0 = 0.52
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.exp(wp.cos(v0 + 0.72)))
    v2 = 0.16
    v2 = v0
    tmp = (tmp * ((v1 + 0.11 / v2 + 0.36) - wp.exp(tmp + 0.78)))
    data[tid] = v0
